org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface ITernaryOperatorNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IExpressionNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TernaryOperatorNode

    public interface ITernaryOperatorNode
extends IExpressionNode
    An AST node representing the ternary operator.

    The typical shape of this node is: 

     ITernaryOperatorNode 
   IExpressionNode <-- getConditionalNode()
   IExpressionNode <-- getLeftOperandNode()
   IExpressionNode <-- getRightOperandNode()
    For example, a == b ? c : d is represented as 
     ITernaryOperatorNode "?"
   IBinaryOperatorNode "=="
     IIdentifierNode "a"
     IIdentifierNode "b"
   IIdentifierNode "c"
   IIdentiferNode "d"
